    "For example, the optimized crystalline structure and the preferential elements in the crystal will be insightful for us to screen promising cathode materials in the future.",
    "Thus, the MP database based on the consistent high-throughput computation has received substantial attention in past years.",
    "It will be more interesting to see a standardized database with high-throughput experimental results based on the wide range of battery categories with specifically designed features to satisfy the predetermined properties, including the voltage, capacity and volume change for next generation of advanced cathodes.",
    "Li metal 47, Silicon (Si) 48 and high entropy oxides 49 have attained much attention besides the widely used carbon(graphite), because of their super high theoretical capacity compared to other anodes.",
    "We notice that Li dendrite growth is the main obstacle to prevent industrialization of Li metal battery."
